|2 |  └─HASH JOIN                    |        |1       |247         |
|3 |    ├─EXCHANGE IN DISTR          |        |283     |212         |
|4 |    │ └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (PKEY)|:EX10000|283     |168         |
|5 |    │   └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR      |        |283     |72          |
|6 |    │     └─TABLE FULL SCAN      |a       |283     |72          |
|7 |    └─PX PARTITION ITERATOR      |        |1       |8           |
|8 |      └─TABLE FULL SCAN          |b       |1       |8           |
=====================================================================
